fields.value: Harvard CGA Geo-tweet Archive - known bots

dsDescriptionValue.value:
These bots appear to be randomly distributed spatially.  These are bots discovered as of 1/15/2018.  Many of these include a number that looks like a hash.  There are likely to be more.

googuns_prod

yodauncut

================================================
Sample query for eliminating bots from a selection:

NOT user_name:(googuns_lulz OR MarsBots OR autoRNG OR AL_FiN_07839216 OR _grammar_ OR equivocagent OR mozatsubot)

text:/do.*n.*/
